Cloneable, Map<String,Object>
public final class Advertiser
extends GenericJson

An AdvertiserResource.

This is the Java data model class that specifies how to parse/serialize into the JSON that is transmitted over HTTP when working with the Google Affiliate Network API. For a detailed explanation see: http://code.google.com/p/google-api-java-client/wiki/Json

Author:
Google, Inc.

getPayoutRank

public String getPayoutRank()
A rank based on commissions paid to publishers over the past 90 days. A number between 1 and 4 where 4 means the top quartile (most money paid) and 1 means the bottom quartile (least money paid). The value returned may be null.

setPayoutRank

public Advertiser setPayoutRank(String payoutRank)

getEpcSevenDayAverage

public Money getEpcSevenDayAverage()
The sum of fees paid to publishers divided by the total number of clicks over the past seven days. Values are multiplied by 100 for display purposes. The value returned may be null.

setEpcSevenDayAverage
